name: Awe 18
description:
100% of proceeds go directly to a smart contract which will distribute the funds to non-military non-profit organisations helping citizens of Ukraine.

A diffuse material with various transparency maps is mapped on an array of 360 squares resembling a layered and twisted torus-like shape.
Texture manipulation and selected viewing angles define each unique image composition.
Single edition, 3600x3600 .jpeg file created with Sketchup (3D modeling) and Vray (rendering).

2022-03-01
